name: It does look like that, but I'm sure you have a good idea what it is
description: In the room sits a blue bird in a jacket and smokes a cigarette, in front of it is a tripod with a film camera. We were caught by surprise by the presence of a staff man, unknown to us until then.  "It does look like that, but I'm sure you have a good idea what it is". I'm very thankful for that, for a moment I wondered if my new friend would stumble upon something.  The word does its job as well, seeing the familiar faces that would come before me.
